<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">* المُسْتَوَى الرَّابِعُ:</span> وَيَشْمَلُ المُتُونَ التَّالِيَةَ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ - الوَرَقَاتُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢ - عُنْوَانُ الحِكَمِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٣ - بُغْيَةُ البَاحِثِ عَنْ جُمَلِ المَوَارِثِ <span style="color:#008000">(الرَّحْبِيَّةُ)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٤ - العَقِيدَةُ الطَّحَاوِيَّةُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#006d98">* المُسْتَوَى الخَامِسُ:</span> وَيَشْمَلُ المُتُونَ التَّالِيَةَ:<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ - بُلُوغُ المَرَامِ مِنْ أَدِلَّةِ الأَحْكَامِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٢ - زَادُ المُسْتَقْنِعِ فِي اخْتِصَارِ المُقْنِعِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٣ - الخُلَاصَةُ فِي النَّحْوِ <span style="color:#008000">(أَلْفِيَّةُ ابْنِ مَالِكٍ)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#006d98">* المُسْتَوَى السَّادِسُ:</span> وَيَشْمَلُ المُتُونَ التَّالِيَةَ:<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١ - الجَامِعُ لِمَا فِي الصَّحِيْحَيْنِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٢ - أَفْرَادُ البُخَارِيِّ وَمُسْلِمٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٣ - الزَّوَائِدُ عَلَى الصَّحِيْحَيْنِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>